WEBVTT

00:01.175 --> 00:02.480
Previously onHalo...

00:02.524 --> 00:04.395
You kidnapped me.

00:04.439 --> 00:05.744
I will explain everything.

00:05.788 --> 00:07.181
-Cortana!

00:07.224 --> 00:09.139
Shutting down neural bridge.

00:09.183 --> 00:10.445
Dr. Halsey was in my home

00:10.488 --> 00:12.186
