-You will save all of us.

01:50.806 --> 01:52.112
Aren'’t you the lucky one.

02:04.733 --> 02:06.474
Actually, I'’m the lucky one.

02:12.436 --> 02:15.570
Stay calm, Kai.
We got you.

02:15.613 --> 02:16.658
We got you.

02:19.878 --> 02:22.142
It'’s wearing off.
Hit her again.

02:22.185 --> 02:24.535
Don'’t fight it, Kai.

02:24.579 --> 02:26.798
-Kai, let go!

02:26.842 --> 02:28.365
Shit!

02:29.888 --> 02:31.803
Pain'’s too much. Again.

02:35.851 --> 02:37.287
It'’s gonna be okay.

02:37.331 --> 02:39.115
That'’s good.

02:39.159 --> 02:40.725
That'’s good, Kai.

02:42.771 --> 02:44.207
Master Chief?

02:44.251 --> 02:45.861
Master Chief, you'’re ill.

02:45.904 --> 02:47.471
Contact with
