02:51.388 --> 02:54.174
I can'’t do that.
It'’s my job to protect you.

02:54.217 --> 02:55.740
You need medical attention.

02:56.828 --> 02:58.569
Chief?

02:59.918 --> 03:01.268
Captain.

03:05.446 --> 03:07.448
Ground sensors were unable

03:07.491 --> 03:10.059
to track the vector
