over Eridanus.

03:13.889 --> 03:15.369
It'’s my fault.

03:15.412 --> 03:16.848
I lost us the artifact, sir.

03:16.892 --> 03:19.895
You saved 150 lives,

03:19.938 --> 03:21.984
