the dead and wounded.

04:21.348 --> 04:23.480
Very well, Lieutenant.
Bring us in.

04:23.524 --> 04:26.309
-Aye, sir.

04:26.353 --> 04:29.094
We'’ll regroup,
come up with a new plan.

04:29.138 --> 04:30.574
Yes, sir.

04:35.013 --> 04:36.972
