06:05.713 --> 06:08.759
Roman 2474 to 2544.

06:08.803 --> 06:11.327
Aeronautic engineer
and ship designer. Hey!

06:11.371 --> 06:12.981
John?

06:13.024 --> 06:15.723
Quinn was no ordinary
shipbuilder.

06:15.766 --> 06:17.899
-He modernized the entire fleet.

06:17.942 --> 06:20.118
-John?
-But his real genius

06:20.162 --> 06:23.252
was in recognizing the limits
to his own intelligence.

06:23.295 --> 06:24.427
Weird, right?

06:24.471 --> 06:26.168
Open this door right now!

06:26.211 --> 06:28.083
Why did you
lock Dr. Halsey in her lab?

06:28.126 --> 06:30.346
See, Quinn knew
that all technology,

06:30.390 --> 06:33.218
