a fail-safe.

06:35.656 --> 06:37.397
He built fail-safes
into all of his tech,

06:37.440 --> 06:39.137
except one.

06:41.401 --> 06:43.490
The UV decontamination system.

06:48.059 --> 06:49.974
-John!

06:50.018 --> 06:51.933
Turns out,

06:51.976 --> 06:54.326
