07:32.582 --> 07:34.149
-I can'’t.
-Sure you can.

07:34.192 --> 07:36.064
-You'’re my fail-safe.
-That'’s not true.

07:36.107 --> 07:38.240
Open the door.

07:38.283 --> 07:39.894
John, open the door
