state of stasis.

07:54.343 --> 07:57.172
I can'’t control you.
You'’re angry and upset.

07:57.215 --> 07:58.739
-John! Please!
-I understand.

07:58.782 --> 08:00.523
You'’re a machine.
You understand nothing.

08:00.567 --> 08:01.785
-John!

08:01.829 --> 08:03.221
-Open the door.
-You do it.

08:03.265 --> 08:04.745
-I can'’t.
-I don'’t believe you!

08:04.788 --> 08:06.268
She only has a few seconds,
John, please.

08:06.311 --> 08:07.878
John!

08:07.922 --> 08:09.489
Open up!

08:10.707 --> 08:14.015
John! No!

08:14.058 --> 08:16.931
-John!
-John, please.

08:19.237 --> 08:20.630
No!

