12:58.865 --> 12:59.953
Mmm.

12:59.996 --> 13:02.390
I'’ve been called worse.

13:02.433 --> 13:04.174
What can I call you?

13:04.218 --> 13:06.089
Makee.

13:07.569 --> 13:09.223
Makee.

13:09.266 --> 13:11.268
You say you were a prisoner
of the Covenant?

13:12.530 --> 13:13.880
For many years.

13:15.446 --> 13:17.448
Please, if the other
keystone is here,

13:17.492 --> 13:19.059
