20:27.051 --> 20:28.314
for years...

20:30.272 --> 20:32.927
while we fought
and killed for you.

20:32.970 --> 20:34.885
Not for me.

20:34.929 --> 20:39.890
Any challenge to the status quo
is always thought to be mad,

20:39.934 --> 20:42.241
bad, and morally reprehensible

20:42.284 --> 20:43.981
until people see
the benefits.

20:44.025 --> 20:45.244
Who knew?

20:48.029 --> 20:49.813
Who was in on it?

20:52.860 --> 20:54.775
When you'’re fighting
an existential war,

20:54.818 --> 20:57.168
people don'’t ask too many
questions, they just...

20:57.212 --> 20:59.606
