20:59.649 --> 21:03.392
And John, you brought them
the results.

21:03.436 --> 21:05.264
That'’s what got us here.

21:05.307 --> 21:09.050
I knew that by encouraging you
to tap into your memories,

21:09.093 --> 21:11.748
that I risked bringing
all of this to light.

21:11.792 --> 21:13.097
But it was worth it.

21:13.141 --> 21:15.274
It was worth it to unlock

21:15.317 --> 21:17.711
the mysteries
of those artifacts.

21:19.887 --> 21:21.323
What mysteries?

21:25.849 --> 21:27.634
Tell me what you know.

21:27.677 --> 21:32.378
They have upended everything
I thought I knew

21:32.421 --> 21:34.684
about our place
in this universe.

21:34.728 --> 21:39.210
There are more secrets hidden,
and you have the key.

21:39.254 --> 21:41.038
John, you have something
inside of you,

21:41.082 --> 21:43.040
some atavistic connection
to this thing

21:43.084 --> 21:44.912
that we'’re calling the Halo.

21:44.955 --> 21:47.306
And I know.

21:47.349 --> 21:49.264
I know that you will
take us there.

21:49.308 --> 21:52.398
And when you do,
we will lead our species

21:52.441 --> 21:54.661
beyond its current limitations.

21:54.704 --> 21:56.837
But you need me to do this.

21:58.882 --> 22:00.841
Let'’s ensure that all
of these sacrifices

22:00.884 --> 22:03.104
have not been in vain.

22:03.147 --> 22:05.541
Let'’s finish what we started.

22:07.804 --> 22:09.110
I'’ll finish.

22:11.678 --> 22:12.722
Without you.

22:42.970 --> 22:44.058
Chief.

22:45.276 --> 22:46.408
I'’m so--

22:46.452 --> 22:48.018
Doctor.

22:48.062 --> 22:49.411
The Covenant prisoner claims

22:49.455 --> 22:51.065
