with the artifact.

22:51.108 --> 22:52.806
-She said that?
-Could you check on that for me?

22:52.849 --> 22:54.068
-Yes.
-Right away.

22:54.111 --> 22:55.374
Yes, Chief.

23:02.903 --> 23:06.167
Chief, Dr. Halsey was right.

23:06.210 --> 23:07.777
The Halo is uncharted

23:07.821 --> 23:10.345
and potentially
very dangerous territory.

23:10.389 --> 23:12.434
Who do you work for,
Cortana?

23:12.478 --> 23:14.218
I don'’t understand
