23:19.136 --> 23:20.573
Right.

23:20.616 --> 23:22.226
I'’ll make it easy for you.

23:22.270 --> 23:24.054
First chance I get,
I'’m cutting you out.

23:24.098 --> 23:25.708
That'’s not a gamble
