23:27.057 --> 23:29.277
It will likely kill you.

23:29.320 --> 23:32.323
Chief, whatever you think
you'’re looking for, I can help.

23:32.367 --> 23:34.238
No, you can'’t!

23:34.282 --> 23:35.936
I'’m here to solve problems.

23:35.979 --> 23:38.242
That is my only purpose.

23:40.331 --> 23:41.637
What do I do now?

23:41.681 --> 23:43.683
Go solve problems.

23:43.726 --> 23:45.075
Galaxy'’s full of them.

23:59.481 --> 24:01.570
Did you tell Riz and Vannak?

24:01.614 --> 24:03.572
Not yet.

24:03.616 --> 24:05.792
Well, they deserve
