24:23.679 --> 24:25.855
John, I-I think--

24:25.899 --> 24:27.074
I'’m working on it.

24:31.905 --> 24:34.124
Halsey wiped the records.

24:34.168 --> 24:36.300
Oh, God.

24:37.693 --> 24:39.739
Everything she told us
