26:00.602 --> 26:02.561
So, what are you offering?

26:04.563 --> 26:07.217
A lab that I'’m opening
at Barrier Moons.

26:07.261 --> 26:08.697
Just for you.

26:10.394 --> 26:12.048
John gets justice.

26:12.092 --> 26:14.311
The committee
gets their scapegoat.

26:14.355 --> 26:16.836
And you get to continue
your research.

26:16.879 --> 26:19.273
And John?

26:19.316 --> 26:21.884
The stewardship
