32:20.808 --> 32:23.289
Blood results
on the Covenant refugee.

32:23.332 --> 32:24.812
Loading.

32:42.351 --> 32:44.614
Bio identification required.

32:56.626 --> 32:58.280
Access denied.

32:59.499 --> 33:01.718
Open blood analysis.

33:11.380 --> 33:12.903
Drama queen.

33:18.170 --> 33:19.649
